'''圣母圣衣朝圣地'''（Santuario della Madonna del Carmine）是一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]教堂，位于意大利南部坎帕尼亚大区城市[[索伦托|索伦托]]的老城区，始建于第二世纪，重建于16世纪<ref name="Storia">{{Cite web|url=http://www.santuariodelcarminesorrento.it/storia.asp|title=La storia del santuario|editor=Nino Cuomo|4=|access-date=2014-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924094212/http://www.santuariodelcarminesorrento.it/storia.asp|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==历史==
[[File:Santuario_della_Madonna_del_Carmine_(Sorrento)_2.JPG|thumb]]
该堂最初建于第二世纪<ref name="Storia"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sorrentocityportal.it/edifici-di-culto-santuario-della-madonna-del-carmine/|title=Edifici di culto - Il santuario della Madonna del Carmine a Sorrento|3=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221231408/http://www.sorrentocityportal.it/edifici-di-culto-santuario-della-madonna-del-carmine/|archivedate=2014-02-21|accessdate=2014-11-26}}</ref><ref name="Holiday">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sorrentoholiday.info/italian/sorrento-carmine.htm|title=Sorrento - Chiesa del Carmine|accessdate=2014-02-15|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827220310/http://www.sorrentoholiday.info/italian/sorrento-carmine.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>,13名基督徒在异教庙宇处被杀<ref name="Storia"/><ref name="Viaggi">{{Cite web|url=http://www.viaggispirituali.it/2011/11/santuario-madonna-del-carmine-sorrento-napoli/|title=La Madonna del Carmine a Sorrento|editor=Paolo Tonini|4=|accessdate=2014-11-26|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920005711/http://www.viaggispirituali.it/2011/11/santuario-madonna-del-carmine-sorrento-napoli/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在16世纪，来自那不勒斯圣母圣衣圣殿的[[加尔默罗会|加尔默罗会]]神父在此重建[[巴洛克|巴洛克]]风格的新堂<ref name="Storia"/>，1572年完成<ref name="Viaggi"/><ref name="Holiday"/><ref name="Holiday"/>。

[[拿破仑|拿破仑]]抵达那不勒斯后，驱逐了加尔默罗会，该堂收归国有。1816年捐赠给索伦托镇<ref name="Storia"/>。1866年，在此填埋河谷兴建广场，使此处由城门外的偏僻之地变为中心区<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sorrentoinfo.it/la-chiesa-del-carmine/|title=Brevi cenni sulla chiesa|editor=Paolo Tonini|accessdate=2014-02-15|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924103851/http://www.sorrentoinfo.it/la-chiesa-del-carmine/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1936年重归加尔默罗会<ref name="Storia"/>。 

